2.text: Disneyland park in Shanghai, China will be opened to the public on 16th June, 2016. It is the sixth Disney theme park in the world.

3.text: The first Disneyland theme park was opened in 1955 in California U.S.A. It was built by the American entrepreneur Walt Disney. At present there are Disneyland parks in Florida, U.S.A., France, Japan, Hong Kong and China.

4.text: Disneyland parks are very popular theme parks among both children and adults. There are many attractions in Disneyland. "Adventureland" is like a remote tropical jungle with jungle cruises and tree houses. Fairy tales come true in "fantasyland." "Tomorrowland" shows us the future with "Rocket to the Moon" and submarine voyages.

5.text: Another great attraction in Disney theme parks is the famous Disney characters like Mickey Mouse, Donald Duck, Goofy and Roger Rabbit.
